91
00:08:26,240 --> 00:08:28,000
- Sakuragi
- Hanamichi.

92
00:08:30,200 --> 00:08:31,060
Chết đi.

93
00:08:32,190 --> 00:08:33,230
- Sakuragi.
- Ryota.

94
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:42,880
Thằng khốn nạn.

95
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,010
Mitsui...

96
00:08:57,930 --> 00:08:59,380
Ryota...

97
